DATA SOURCES AND ATTRIBUTION
=============================

Admission data was collected and curated from publicly available sources:

    * GradCafe (https://www.thegradcafe.com/)
      - Self-reported graduate admission results
      - Used under fair use for research and educational purposes

    * QuantNet (https://quantnet.com/)
      - MFE program rankings and admission discussions
      - Rankings data (C) QuantNet, used with attribution

    * Reddit (https://www.reddit.com/)
      - r/FinancialEngineering, r/QuantFinance
      - User-submitted content under Reddit's terms of service

    * 1point3acres (https://www.1point3acres.com/)
      - Chinese-language admission result reports
      - Used under fair use for research and educational purposes

    * LinkedIn (https://www.linkedin.com/)
      - Publicly available alumni profile data (930 records)
      - Aggregated and anonymized; no individual PII retained

Program information compiled from:

    * QuantNet 2026 MFE Rankings
    * Official university program websites
    * Public STEM OPT designation databases


